This is a slightly improved version of https://gitlab.com/Tanish2002/st-tanish2002/-/raw/master/patches/0001-add-st-sixel.patch for st 0.9. I did not create this diff myself.

Note that this patch conflicts with the alpha patch, see my other patch for an alpha version.

